downloadTitle: MVP Session 22: Design Network and Rack Diagrams in Visio 2010 (working files)
downloadDescription: Practice creating network and rack diagrams in Microsoft Visio 2010 with these diagrams, part of the Visio 2010 MVP Sessions, Video 22.
detailsSection: Practice creating network and rack diagrams in Visio 2010 with these diagrams, created as companions to the Visio 2010 MVP Sessions (http://visio.microsoft.com/MVPSessions), Video 22. MVP Sessions Video 22 covers the basics of using the Network template in Visio 2010 to quickly and easily create network and rack diagrams. Use these working files to follow along with the video and practice working with the built-in functionality, such as the Legend shape, which will automatically inventory all shapes on the canvas for you.
installInstructionSection: Click Download to save the working files to your computer and then open them with Visio 2010.
additionalInformationSection: Watch the Design Network and Rack Diagrams video (http://visio.microsoft.com/en-us/Get_Started/How_To/Pages/Session-22-Design-network-and-rack-diagrams.aspx).
